\int_{q_{0}}^{q}\mathrm{d}q & = & q-q_{0}=\frac{1}{\left(1+g_{2}/g_{1}\right)\frac{l}{L}}\left[\int_{n_{i0}}^{n_{i}}\frac{\mathrm{d}n_{i}}{n_{i}}-\int_{n_{i0}}^{n_{i}}\mathrm{d}n_{i}\right]\\
