\end_inset 

por lo tanto
\begin_inset Formula \[
\frac{P_{p}}{E_{s}}=\frac{L}{l}\frac{\frac{n_{i0}}{n_{iu}}-\left(1+\ln\frac{n_{i0}}{n_{iu}}\right)}{t_{c}\phi\frac{n_{i0}}{n_{iu}}}\]

